Homework 2 Readme File

Basic Information
PLATFORM: OSX
OS Version: OSX Yosemite 10.10.1
Build Environment: Xcode
Build Environment Version: Xcode 6.1.1
Language: C++
External Libraries Used (e.g., GLUT, GL, etc.): GLUT, GL, GLU, math.h, ctime, stdio, stdlib, iostream, fstream

Build Instructions
1. Unzip File
2. Open Folder "MP2FlightSimulator"
3. Open File "MP2FlightSimulatorFinal.xcodeproj"
4. Make Sure "main.cpp" is the only Compile Source in "Build Phases"
4. Run

OR

Simply run the Executable
1. Unzip File
2. Open Folder "MP2FlightSimulator"
3. Open Folder "MP1FlightSimulatorFinal"
4. Double Click Executable "MP2FlightSimulatorFinal"

Controls
‘w’ - Pitch Up
‘a’ - Roll Left
’s’ - Pitch Down
‘d’ - Roll Right
‘+’ - Raise Sea Level
‘-‘ - Lower Sea Level

